IBM Boosts Dividend, Authorizes $8 Billion for Stock Repurchases

-- B y   B i l l   K o e n i g
-- 
2011-04-26T14:22:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/ibm-boosts-dividend-authorizes-8-billion-for-stock-repurchases.html
International Business Machines
Corp. (IBM)  said its board approved a 15 percent increase in its
quarterly stock dividend and authorized $8 billion for stock
purchases.  The company declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of
75 cents a share, an increase of 10 cents a share. The dividend
is payable June 10 to shareholders of record on May 10.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bill Koenig at 
 wkoenig@bloomberg.net  